text: "Did I Tell You" is the fourth single released by The Spinto Band, as well as the fourth single from the album Nice and Nicely Done. "Did I Tell You" was the first single by The Spinto Band to be on the charts, reaching #55 in the UK. ==External links== * Category:2005 singles Category:2005 songs Category:The Spinto Band songs
title: Did I Tell You (The Spinto Band song)
